	(11,'4','Capabilities','{"title": "ZGCC/ZIM Capabilities", "article": "<div>\\n  <p>\\n    More than 3,000 skilled employees and professional teams have focused on the\\n    production for over 50 years. We have a nationally certified inspection\\n    center. We cover raw materials to finish parts for consistency,\\n    repeatability, and superiority, which are guaranteed. An advance MIS system\\n    and RD capability to serve the customer with rapid response and turn-key\\n    solutions. A complete production line of Tungsten and Molybdenum to have\\n    every process under control.\\n  </p>\\n  <p>\\n    We offer advanced testing and examination equipment, first-class raw\\n    material production and the use of advanced production equipment.\\n  </p>\\n</div>\\n", "gallery": [{"id": 21, "file": "MaC2A5L4WSK1vkxXHfXyyTOvg.webp", "name": "pobrane (1).jpeg", "mimetype": "jpeg", "thumbnail": "0eD2nz5MGIOwCIJTs8iBbZnNZ.webp"}, {"id": 22, "file": "0NeOUqAQtHXaIh19hTF15myzO.webp", "name": "pobrane (2).jpeg", "mimetype": "jpeg", "thumbnail": "iCYM2zE9Gf2wYANU0QBRZwvIF.webp"}, {"id": 23, "file": "Oi27eIf51BD1yJerU6XV9pF8d.webp", "name": "pobrane (3).jpeg", "mimetype": "jpeg", "thumbnail": "sNXEkQrEZcWhowYhJ3wD3Q0sj.webp"}, {"id": 26, "file": "wm282jpArZmFBR1rOay701gXj.webp", "name": "pobrane (4).jpeg", "mimetype": "jpeg", "thumbnail": "FGgbwsGiTqIF5G5iUrXmcoRN2.webp"}, {"id": 27, "file": "9USPWJ0fLoTVXjylQUN8ec8Hh.webp", "name": "pobrane (5).jpeg", "mimetype": "jpeg", "thumbnail": "hs4ytt8R4yZWhwenA8fEw3rBS.webp"}, {"id": 24, "file": "SM7MiX1jvqdClyll5HWZ9Eo3k.webp", "name": "pobrane (6).jpeg", "mimetype": "jpeg", "thumbnail": "i2Udl04q0Gxi9rT6xVyahGZhV.webp"}, {"id": 29, "file": "7kuZrYN2ZJa3zv8ArnebP0YjH.webp", "name": "pobrane (7).jpeg", "mimetype": "jpeg", "thumbnail": "eWcvUuZ7Ck5nYcTwTjo54IoNt.webp"}, {"id": 25, "file": "rCrTtH00o7jX9z33ZJknJRcfD.webp", "name": "pobrane (8).jpeg", "mimetype": "jpeg", "thumbnail": "IpLQaObCrXBZJ34vrqN9aZfbW.webp"}, {"id": 28, "file"