	(4,2,'Tlenek wolframu.','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p><strong><img class=\\\\\\"wp-image-1408 alignleft\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\"float: left;\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\"https://zim-llc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/tungsten-oxide-powder.jpg\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\"\\\\\\" width=\\\\\\"210\\\\\\" height=\\\\\\"107\\\\\\" loading=\\\\\\"lazy\\\\\\" />Yellow Tungsten Oxide:&nbsp;</strong></p>\\\\n<p>Yellow Tungsten oxide is a crystallized powder. The color is uniform and unanimous. There are no mechanical impurities and agglomerates visible.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Blue Tungsten Oxide:</strong></p>\\\\n<p>Blue tungsten oxide powder is a deep blue or dark blue crystallized powder. The color is uniform and unanimous. There are no mechanical impurities and agglomerates visible.</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":37,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"iXU9YKDJistMlCWmNpvYkLK8n.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Powder-Production-of-Tungsten-oxide-compressed.pdf\\",\\"description\\":null,\\"file\\":\\"ciuidN480mznT7eciJXnt9NqX.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\"}],\\"key\\":1}]}"',1,1,NULL,'2021-03-10 13:29:34','2021-03-10 13:40:19'),
	(5,2,'Оксид вольфрама','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p><strong><img class=\\\\\\"wp-image-1408 alignleft\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\"float: left;\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\"https://zim-llc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/tungsten-oxide-powder.jpg\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\"\\\\\\" width=\\\\\\"210\\\\\\" height=\\\\\\"107\\\\\\" loading=\\\\\\"lazy\\\\\\" />Yellow Tungsten Oxide:&nbsp;</strong></p>\\\\n<p>Yellow Tungsten oxide is a crystallized powder. The color is uniform and unanimous. There are no mechanical impurities and agglomerates visible.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Blue Tungsten Oxide:</strong></p>\\\\n<p>Blue tungsten oxide powder is a deep blue or dark blue crystallized powder. The color is uniform and unanimous. There are no mechanical impurities and agglomerates visible.</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":37,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"iXU9YKDJistMlCWmNpvYkLK8n.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Powder-Production-of-Tungsten-oxide-compressed.pdf\\",\\"description\\":null,\\"file\\":\\"ciuidN480mznT7eciJXnt9NqX.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\"}],\\"key\\":1}]}"',1,3,NULL,'2021-03-10 13:29:34','2021-03-10 13:40:28'),
	(6,2,'Tungsten Oxide','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p><strong><img class=\\\\\\"wp-image-1408 alignleft\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\"float: left;\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\"https://zim-llc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/tungsten-oxide-powder.jpg\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\"\\\\\\" width=\\\\\\"210\\\\\\" height=\\\\\\"107\\\\\\" loading=\\\\\\"lazy\\\\\\" />Yellow Tungsten Oxide:&nbsp;</strong></p>\\\\n<p>Yellow Tungsten oxide is a crystallized powder. The color is uniform and unanimous. There are no mechanical impurities and agglomerates visible.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Blue Tungsten Oxide:</strong></p>\\\\n<p>Blue tungsten oxide powder is a deep blue or dark blue crystallized powder. The color is uniform and unanimous. There are no mechanical impurities and agglomerates visible.</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":37,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"iXU9YKDJistMlCWmNpvYkLK8n.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Powder-Production-of-Tungsten-oxide-compressed.pdf\\",\\"description\\":null,\\"file\\":\\"ciuidN480mznT7eciJXnt9NqX.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\"}],\\"key\\":1}]}"',1,2,NULL,'2021-03-10 13:29:34','2021-03-10 13:40:03'),
	(7,3,'Вольфрамовые металлические порошки','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p><img class=\\\\\\"wp-image-1418 alignleft\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\"float: left;\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\"https://zim-llc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/tungsten-powder-image.jpg\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\"\\\\\\" width=\\\\\\"146\\\\\\" height=\\\\\\"74\\\\\\" loading=\\\\\\"lazy\\\\\\" />ZGCC manufactures a wide range of particle sizes with multiple physical properties for different applications. Tungsten Carbide has a high purity (&gt;99.9%), excellent dispersity, and wide adaptability.</p>\\\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Appearance:</strong>uniform gray metallic powder</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Particle size:</strong>&nbsp;0.2-60&mu;m<br />Super Fine (BET&gt;5, 0.6-0.8&mu;m): W: 99.9%, O: 0.6%max<br />Sub-Fine (0.8-1.0&mu;m): W: 99.9%, O: 0.25%max<br />Fine (1.0-2.5&mu;m): W: 99.9%, O: 0.20%max<br />Medium Fine (2.5-8.0&mu;m): W: 99.9%, O: 0.08%max<br />Coarse (8.0-15.0&mu;m): W: 99.9%, O: 0.06%max<br />Extra Coarse (15.0-25.0&mu;m): W: 99.9%, O: 0.08%max<br />Super Coarse (25.0-60.0&mu;m): W: 99.9%, O: 0.15%max</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Application:</strong></p>\\\\n<p>It can be used as a raw material to manufacture Tungsten Carbide powder, High Density Alloy and other crystalline Tungsten powder (shoulder powder), and other Tungsten products.</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":39,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"Oi8BjqcbDzY8eDsQ1dqHzvWFd.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Tungsten-Powder.pdf\\",\\"description\\":null,\\"file\\":\\"GDofkF69JWZSmTJiNugDmTjJg.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\"}],\\"key\\":1}]}"',1,3,NULL,'2021-03-10 13:44:04','2021-03-10 18:34:03'),
