	(10,4,'Урошок карбида вольфрама','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p><img class=\\\\\\"wp-image-1424 alignleft\\\\\\" src=\\\\\\"https://zim-llc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/tungsten-carbide-powder-image.jpg\\\\\\" sizes=\\\\\\"(max-width: 201px) 100vw, 201px\\\\\\" srcset=\\\\\\"https://zim-llc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/tungsten-carbide-powder-image.jpg 484w, https://zim-llc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/tungsten-carbide-powder-image-300x147.jpg 300w\\\\\\" alt=\\\\\\"\\\\\\" width=\\\\\\"201\\\\\\" height=\\\\\\"98\\\\\\" loading=\\\\\\"lazy\\\\\\" />ZGCC manufactures a wide range of particle sizes with multiple physical properties for different applications. Tungsten Carbide powder has a high purity, centralized particle size distribution, perfect crystal morphology and stable quality.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Appearance:<br /></strong>Dark gray or light gray with uniform and unanimous color.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Size:&nbsp;</strong>0.2 ~ 60&mu;m</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Application:<br /></strong>The Tungsten Carbide powder is mainly used as raw material to manufacture Cemented Carbide products including cutting tools, mining tools, Tungsten-based hardfacing materials, and other wear parts.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Common Tungsten Carbide Powder:<br /></strong>This series of Tungsten powder has a stable quality and can meet the requirements of most Cemented Carbide production. It is the most widely used Tungsten Carbide powder.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Superfine Tungsten Carbide Powder:<br /></strong>This series of Tungsten Carbide powder has a good centralized particle size distribution, excellent dispersity, low sensitivity to alloy sintering temperature, moderate oxygen content, and high hardness.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Sub-fine Tungsten Carbide:<br /></strong>This series of Tungsten Carbide powder has centralized size particle distribution, excellent dispersion low oxygen content, and stable quality.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Super Coarse Tungsten Carbide:<br /></strong>This series of Tungsten Carbide powder has a perfect grain structure and excellent particle morphology.</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":41,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"uNuwLVcE9zMxCJzxCGKHa0vo6.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Tungsten-Carbide-Powder-compressed.pdf\\",\\"file\\":\\"vm48bHKcgRifySw0CwZ7wsgKT.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\",\\"updatedAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T18:37:10.494Z\\",\\"createdAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T18:37:10.494Z\\"}],\\"key\\":1}]}"',1,3,NULL,'2021-03-10 18:38:30','2021-03-10 18:38:30'),
