	(28,10,'Цементированный карбид для добычи','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p>Tungsten Carbides are mainly mined for making various mining and construction tools. They are widely used in mining, engineering construction, road construction, and many other fields.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Carbide tips for Milling:</strong></p>\\\\n<p>These kind of tips are used for rock cutting and milling with large consumption.<br />&bull; Carbide tips for road milling<br />&bull; Carbide tips for rotary drill rigging<br />&bull; Carbide tips for coal mining<br />&bull; Carbide tips for tunneling<br />&bull; Carbide tips for trenching</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Carbide tips for Drilling:</strong></p>\\\\n<p>These kind of tips are used with an impactor to drill holes in rock.<br />&bull; Carbide tips for rock down-hole drilling<br />&bull; Carbide tips for mine drilling<br />&bull; Carbide tips for tri-cone bits<br />&bull; Carbide tips for rock drilling bits<br />&bull; Carbide tips for oil drilling tri-cone bits</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Diamond substrate</strong><br />&bull; Carbide Tips for Geological Prospecting</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":58,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"CcOvNmMVVCcYz0yzMsmx2y4y6.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Mining-Carbide-2016.pdf\\",\\"file\\":\\"HZXOw3hWFkJmYQTFB6vg3VyEA.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\",\\"updatedAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T19:21:09.305Z\\",\\"createdAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T19:21:09.305Z\\"}],\\"key\\":1}]}"',2,3,NULL,'2021-03-10 19:21:40','2021-03-10 19:21:40'),
