	(40,14,'Narzędzia górnicze i budowlane','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p>The newly developed Carbide tips use a super coarse, optimized grain size of Tungsten Carbide to improve the impact resistance and fatigue crack resistance. With the professional shape design, optimal Tungsten Carbide material, strictly controlled steel body, our cutting bits and milling bits show an exceptional life cycle and can significantly reduce your operating costs.</p>\\\\n<p>&bull; Cutting Bits for Mining tools<br />&bull; Road Milling and Planning Tools</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":66,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"CMuhAtF9Q4kfnIz1li5GXfQwJ.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Cutting-Bits-For-Mining.pdf\\",\\"file\\":\\"JbM8jp9mooDtlAq6gAUyeavce.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\",\\"updatedAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T19:33:38.037Z\\",\\"createdAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T19:33:38.037Z\\"},{\\"id\\":67,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"XD5627EDTGUKufAaDFIB9clNf.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Road-Milling-And-Planning-Tools.pdf\\",\\"file\\":\\"g20qbMzpA7ZBQg69jSwIaLWy3.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\",\\"updatedAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T19:34:39.078Z\\",\\"createdAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T19:34:39.078Z\\"}],\\"key\\":1}]}"',2,1,NULL,'2021-03-10 19:35:34','2021-03-10 19:35:34'),
