	(44,15,'Tungsten Carbide HardFacing Materiał','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p><strong>Tungsten Carbide Hardfacing Material</strong><br />We manufacture three types of cast Tungsten Carbide powder including, Cast (Fused) Tungsten Carbide powder, Spherical Cast (Fused) Tungsten Carbide powder, and Macrocrystalline (Mono) Tungsten Carbide powder.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Cast (Fused) Tungsten Carbide (CTC)</strong><br />CTC is made of W and WC and is an extremely hard, wear-resistant material. It is widely used to produce premixed powder for PTA &amp; LC, PDC Matrix Powder, tubular welding rod.</p>\\\\n<p>&bull; High content, feather-like micro structure, as high as 95%.<br />&bull; High hardness: 2000HV0.1 min<br />&bull; A wide particle size range to choose from: 8-600mesh (2360-25&mu;m)<br />&bull; Excellent weldability with other Ni-based and Fe-based binder</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Spherical Cast (Fused) Tungsten Carbide (SCTC)</strong><br />ZTC uses proprietary equipment and techniques to manufacture SCTC powder. SCTC has a dendritic crystal microstructure composed of WC and W2C. It has a higher hardness (2700HV 0.1) than conventional CTC.</p>\\\\n<p>&bull; The first manufacturer in China<br />&bull; A wide particle size range to choose from: 60-325mesh (250-45&mu;m)<br />&bull; Excellent Hall Flow ability due to high sphericity<br />&bull; Widely used in Laser Cladding and PTA</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Macrocrystalline (Mono) Tungsten Carbide (MTC)</strong><br />MTC is a fully carbonized, dense, light gray Tungsten Carbide powder with a homogenous microstructure and excellent thermal stability. It is made from precisely chosen raw materials and special alloys.</p>\\\\n<p>&bull; Coarse grain size<br />&bull; Excellent combined erosion and impact resistance<br />&bull; Hardness: 1600-2000HV0.1<br />&bull; Widely used as hard phases in PDC Matrix powder, premixed powder for PTA, and Laser Cladding</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":68,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"dwtKaVACxRPYWuSbm40gjuZfP.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Tungsten-Carbide-Hardfacing-Material.pdf\\",\\"file\\":\\"eR6PbAosWq4Bmknf8ELblnkk7.pdf\\",\\"mimetype\\":\\"pdf\\",\\"updatedAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T19:44:56.199Z\\",\\"createdAt\\":\\"2021-03-10T19:44:56.199Z\\"}],\\"key\\":1}]}"',3,1,NULL,'2021-03-10 19:46:07','2021-03-10 19:46:07'),
