	(52,18,'Materiały spawalnicze','"{\\"article\\":\\"\\",\\"sections\\":[{\\"article\\":\\"<p>ZGCC manufactures a wide range of products for customized wear solutions. The most widely used products include flexible rope, composite rod, tubular welding rod for oxygen-acetylene gas welding, different types of premixed powder for flame spray, laser cladding, and Plasma Transferred Arc (PTA) welding.</p>\\\\n<p><a href=\\\\\\"https://zim-llc.com/contact-us/\\\\\\">Contact us&nbsp;</a>if you have any questions.</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Flexible rope</strong><br />&bull; Cast Tungsten Carbide (CTC), Spherical Cast Tungsten Carbide (SCTC) with Nickel binder<br />&bull; Excellent weldability<br />&bull; Diameters of 4.0mm, 6.0mm, 8.0mm are available<br />&bull; 15Kgs/coil<br /><strong>&bull; Application:</strong>&nbsp;steel body bit blade, oil extraction part</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Composite rod</strong><br />&bull; Made of high quality, recycled carbide grits and NiCu alloy binder<br />&bull; Wide carbide size range: 1/16&rsquo;&rsquo;- 1&rsquo;&rsquo;<br />&bull; Sharp carbide edges<br /><strong>&bull; Application:</strong>&nbsp;milling and fishing tools (reamer)</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Tubular welding rod</strong><br />&bull; CTC, MTC, SCTC, and Carbide Pellets are used<br /><strong>&bull; Diameter:</strong>&nbsp;3.2mm~6.4mm<br /><strong>&bull; Length:</strong>&nbsp;600mm~900mm<br /><strong>&bull; Application:</strong>&nbsp;feed grinder hammer, blades of steel body oil bits</p>\\\\n<p><strong>Premixed Powder<br /></strong>ZGCC uses one or a combination of different sizes of CTC, MTC, SCTC as hard phases to blend with different hardnesses of Nickel Alloy (NiBSi, NiCrBSi) to produce dozens of premixed powders for different applications.</p>\\\\n<p>We can tailor make the premixed powder per customer&rsquo;s specifications.</p>\\",\\"files\\":[{\\"id\\":74,\\"thumbnail\\":\\"HylTwxbGaJmzbhCKk5iuuIWqu.webp\\",\\"name\\":\\"Welding-Materials.pdf\\",\\"description\\":null,\\"file\\":\\"fLKe4LT